text: Trond Jensrud Trond Jensrud (born 2 September 1968 in Ringerike) is a Norwegian politician for the Labour Party. He was elected to the Norwegian Parliament from Buskerud in 1989, but was not re-elected in 1993. He was also a member of Buskerud county council in 1995-1996\. ==References== Category:1968 births Category:Living people Category:Labour Party (Norway) politicians Category:Members of the Storting Category:People from Ringerike (municipality) Category:20th-century Norwegian politicians
